title: Add /context slash command for session and context info
---
There is no built-in slash command to display current session info: token usage, % of context window used, compaction thresholds, session ID, channel, and other runtime metadata. Users have no quick way to inspect their context budget. Add a /context command that surfaces this information in-channel.